name: Change
description: Lindsay Kemp was a legendary performance artist and dancer who mentored David Bowie and choreographed the theatrical production of Ziggy Stardust in 1972.  I had the great privilege of working with Lindsay many times and directed him in this beautiful performance of him miming to each meaning of each word in the lyrics of my song 'Change'. More of our work together can be found here:https://bit.ly/32YlGn0
